**Segments**

- The flexible and semi-rigid ureteroscopy market can be segmented based on product type, application, end-user, and region. In terms of product type, the market is divided into flexible ureteroscopes and semi-rigid ureteroscopes. Flexible ureteroscopes are preferred for their ability to access difficult-to-reach areas with less discomfort to the patient. Semi-rigid ureteroscopes, on the other hand, are more rigid and provide better control during the procedure. The application segment includes urolithiasis, kidney cancer, ureteral stricture, and others. End-users of flexible and semi-rigid ureteroscopes are hospitals, specialty clinics, ambulatory surgical centers, and others.

